  m_Text: "To any loyal ears that remain\u2026\nThe Rebels prepare to strike first.\nThey
    plan to burn the outer Army posts by nightfall,\nand then push into the city
    under the chaos.\n\nIf you wear the Army\u2019s uniform in silence,\nknow this:
    one choice can tip the war.\nChoose wisely\u2026 before either side discovers
    you"
